title: Freaky Friday: How often do you watch porn?
itunes:title: Freaky Friday: How often do you watch porn?
description:
Friday 6/1- Today on the show we had comedian Neal Brennan stop by, where he spoke about new projects, being in between rap beefs, and did you know he watches porn everyday? Well because of that confession he made, it was only right for Freaky Friday that we made that into a topic, so we opened up the phone lines to see how often our listeners watched porn, and you can tell some of our callers have way too much time on their hands. Moreover, after the Cavs and Warriors game last night and JR Smith making questionable moves the whole time during the game Charlamagne gave JR Smith "Donkey of the Day".
